  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dcf \u0d91\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gota will come on Saturday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa is scheduled to return to the island next Saturday. In view of the strong public protest against the President on July 9, the former President first left for the Maldives and then for Singapore.",
        "While in Singapore, the President announced his resignation from office and due to exceeding the time he could stay there, he left Singapore for Thailand.",
        "According to the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna's request to the President to provide the necessary facilities for the former President to return to Sri Lanka, the necessary facilities have been provided for him to return to Sri Lanka."
      ],
